author: Jason Brennan
title: TV | Live UEFA Champions League - Arsenal vs Bayern Munich
text: Arsenal host Bayern Munich in this group stage clash at 7.45pm in The Emirates. Having lost both opening games to Dinamo Zagreb and Olympiakos, Arsene Wenger's side will need to pull and unlikely win out of the bag if they are to have any chance of getting in the knockout stages. Bayern on the other hand, enter the game as hot favourites after recording to wins in their opening games, as well as rolling through the German Bundesliga so far this season. If Arsenal turn up like they have done in their two previous games, the white-hot Robert Lewandowski will have a field day.
